quote.summary: XiAn Kingfar Property Services Co Ltd is a China-based company mainly engaged in city services and property management services. The Company has three main businesses. The city services mainly provide public property management services, municipal management services and municipal value-added services. Public properties include government buildings, education institutes and hospitals. Municipal properties includes public facilities and infrastructure. Municipal value-added services cover government buildings. The residential property management services provide basic property management services and value-added services for residential properties. The commercial property management services provide basic property management services and value-added services for office buildings, industrial parks and factories. The Company mainly conducts business in the domestic market.
